headline: Macquarie Wealth Builder Fund Q2 2025 Commentary
summary: For 2Q25, Macquarie Wealth Builder Fund Institutional Class shares underperformed the Fund's benchmark, a blend of 60% S&P 500 Index and 40% Bloomberg US Aggregate Index.
